{"tid":1469190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你飛接機，set deadline，ATC罷工","createTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:23:09.000Z","uid":59559,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"96833f216bf90e256a258e63501709eaebfba711","tid":1469190,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:13.000Z","msg":"禁制令已出<br />\n可以喺指定範圍內和你飛<br />\n<br />\n<ins>和你飛</ins><br />\n建議五大訴求有咁大隻得咁大隻<br />\n要旅客一出嚟就見到<br />\n要簡單直接<br />\n警察暴力都要，但唔好係成個示威嘅唯一焦點<br />\n勇武其他地方爬山<br />\n<br />\n<ins>Set deadline</ins><br />\n如果deadline前得唔到滿意回應<br />\n預告下一次罷工<br />\n請ATC預告會參與下一次罷工<br />\n罷工影響機場運作冇得ban喇掛"},{"pid":"8f8c1084b6ab4455e727c705488cb1274efe7817","tid":1469190,"uid":59559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"大家點睇"},{"pid":"948477d121256ac81cbefbea7e47f95ea5a58607","tid":1469190,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:00:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"070c1565993d0dc4a26d2776c0d410dce184ac1d","tid":1469190,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:02:25.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"5d979dd76b8af46cafd94c52e8948c5980d09a38","tid":1469190,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:04:33.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"86e1a689fae1361048f12d4868e722540ef9c3bd","tid":1469190,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"ae4c25c8bfc48aa8f70a54d92fa1fb4f252b2523","tid":1469190,"uid":59559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:05:01.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3d9dc640acbf996ac04146b8122b4363406e1de7","tid":1469190,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:05:17.000Z","msg":"塞旅客就一定要塞，如果唔係出機場做咩？塞嘅話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。"},{"pid":"c3f269d671a63ccfc5cb9339303e1d55e19d090f